Localization.Name: Snaggle Stick (Original)
Localization.Description:
NDR: 14
Effects: Hypertrophic, Dehydrating

Snag one of these premium protein sticks and experience the ultimate in "real meat" snacking. Original Snaggle sticks feature a classic blend of smoke and spices for a pure boost of flavor energy.
